original_title: Hip Hop Abs - Secrets to Flat Abs & Fat Burning Cardio
overview: Shaun shares his exclusive training techniques that target your upper abs, lower abs, and obliques while you burn fat. Just Tilt, Tuck & Tighten and you're on your way to a flat, sexy midsection.  This is not your mama's aerobic video. Burn calories and shed fat with fun, hip dance moves and hot music you hear on the radio.
title: Hip Hop Abs - Secrets to Flat Abs & Fat Burning Cardio
